    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a reliable ride that's been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure, you've found it! This beauty runs great and has plenty of life left in it. It's got a few tiny signs of character here and there, but overall it's in really solid shape and super clean inside. I've absolutely loved driving this car, and I know you will too! Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. Come take it for a spin!",
