    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2008 BMW M3 (E92) is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 era. Featuring an 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies, the powertrain delivers linear throttle response and 414 hp. This unit is equipped with the M-DCT dual-clutch transmission for rapid-fire shifts and the factory carbon-fiber roof to reduce polar moment of inertia. Key maintenance items, including rod bearings and throttle actuators, have been proactively addressed. The chassis retains its rigidity, supported by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a Variable M Differential Lock. A well-maintained driver's car that balances track-ready engineering with daily usability.",
